BT /F1 10 Tf 54 248 Td (Use Gap only to show only scenes that still cover part of the AOI not already covered by kept scenes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 234 Td (This is useful for large AOIs where several scenes are needed. The list updates as you keep or reject) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 220 Td (scenes.) Tj ET
