BT /F1 10 Tf 54 154 Td (Leaflet layer checklist so overlapping kept images can be switched on and off individually for a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 140 Td (final visual check. Use All and None in that Leaflet checklist to quickly show or hide every kept) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 126 Td (image layer.) Tj ET
